# data_fetcher crontab  (supercronic format – same as standard cron)
#
# Fetch prices + KPIs every trading day at 18:30 CET (17:30 UTC) – after market close
# Also run a quick refresh at 09:00 UTC for pre-market data
#
# min  hour  day  month  weekday   command
  30   17    *    *      1-5       python /app/data_fetcher.py --mode full
   0    9    *    *      1-5       python /app/data_fetcher.py --mode prices
